rComments: Such a great professor! Professor Marwa is really kind, and she gives patience in her feedback. Students will get a lot help from her. Her lecture is comprehensive, including the each steps from the examples. Tests are OK for me, as long as you listen and watch videos carefully, you will get a good result!

While her midterm was very fair, the final was extremely hard and very different than homework questions and concepts focused on. For this reason, I would choose a different professor that better prepares their students for the final, by for example assigning homework questions that actually prepares one for the final.

Such a Kind professor. She is very understanding! Test are completely based on the text book so I would definitelly read the chapters, and assignments are very straigth forward! She is a fair proff!! would deffo take her again!
